---
import { User, Share, LucideVerified, School } from "@lucide/astro";
---

<footer
  class="bg-academic-charcoal text-white pt-24 pb-12 px-6 lg:px-20 border-t-8 border-primary"
>
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto">
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-4 gap-16 mb-20">
      <div class="col-span-1 md:col-span-2">
        <div class="flex items-center gap-4 mb-8">
          <div
            class="size-12 bg-primary rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center text-white"
          >
            <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-3xl">
              <School />
            </span>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-900 tracking-tight">
            SECUNDARIA GENERAL NO. 10
          </h3>
        </div>
        <p class="text-slate-400 text-lg max-w-md mb-8">
          Formando con excelencia académica y valores desde el corazón de la
          Comarca Lagunera. Un legado de educación pública de calidad en
          Torreón, Coahuila.
        </p>
        <div class="flex gap-4">
          <a
            class="w-12 h-12 rounded-xl bg-white/5 flex items-center justify-center hover:bg-primary transition-all"
            href="#"
          >
            <User />
          </a>
          <a
            class="w-12 h-12 rounded-xl bg-white/5 flex items-center justify-center hover:bg-primary transition-all"
            href="#"
          >
            <Share />
          </a>
          <a
            class="w-12 h-12 rounded-xl bg-white/5 flex items-center justify-center hover:bg-primary transition-all"
            href="#"
          >
            <LucideVerified />
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div>
        <h4
          class="font-black text-primary text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.3em] mb-8"
        >
          Explora
        </h4>
        <ul class="space-y-4">
          <li>
            <a
              class="text-slate-400 hover:text-white transition-colors font-medium"
              href="#inicio">Página Principal</a
            >
          </li>
          <li>
            <a
              class="text-slate-400 hover:text-white transition-colors font-medium"
              href="#nosotros">Identidad Institucional</a
            >
          </li>
          <li>
            <a
              class="text-slate-400 hover:text-white transition-colors font-medium"
              href="#oferta">Programas de Estudio</a
            >
          </li>
          <li>
            <a
              class="text-slate-400 hover:text-white transition-colors font-medium"
              href="#instalaciones">Nuestras Áreas</a
            >
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      <div>
        <h4
          class="font-black text-primary text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.3em] mb-8"
        >
          Administrativo
        </h4>
        <ul class="space-y-4">
          <li>
            <a
              class="text-slate-400 hover:text-white transition-colors font-medium"
              href="#">Proceso de Inscripción</a
            >
          </li>
          <li>
            <a
              class="text-slate-400 hover:text-white transition-colors font-medium"
              href="#">Becas y Apoyos</a
            >
          </li>
          <li>
            <a
              class="text-slate-400 hover:text-white transition-colors font-medium"
              href="#">Calendario Escolar</a
            >
          </li>
          <li>
            <a
              class="text-slate-400 hover:text-white transition-colors font-medium"
              href="#">Aviso de Privacidad</a
            >
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div
      class="pt-8 border-t border-white/5 flex flex-col md:flex-row justify-between items-center gap-4 text-sm text-slate-500"
    >
      <p>
        © 2024 Escuela Secundaria General No. 10 Netzahualcóyotl. Torreón,
        Coahuila.
      </p>
      <p class="font-bold text-slate-400 tracking-widest uppercase text-[10px]">
        C.C.T. 05DES0010X
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</footer>
